column1: Bosscat Kitchen & Libations////The resturant was really cute!!! Love the DJ and the atmosphere.  Service was outstanding
column2: I was with a large group and Terry (our server) was amazing!!!! He handle the group with grace
column3: not allowing our drinks to get low.....he was attentive!!! Terry also had an amazing personality!!! I would definitely return
column5: wasn't that impressed with the food.
